      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"different perspective\" thing is just a way to sugarcoat reality. It's not a perspective issue, it's just the truth. There is no grand plan, no destiny, just entropy. Every bit of effort I put into \"finding meaning\" is just a distraction from the fact that everything eventually goes dark and stays dark. It's exhausting pretending there's a point to any of it.",
